title: Grateful Dead Live at Shrine Auditorium on 1976-10-14
lineage: Analog Sound Preservation: MAC ->  CR7A -> Audio Technica AM 400 Line Amp/mixer -> Korg MR 2000 at 5.6 mhz
description:
Set I
Promised Land
They Love Each Other
Cassidy
Peggy-O
Big River
Ramble On Rose
Looks Like Rain
Deal
El Paso
Tennessee Jed
The Music Never Stopped
Scarlet Begonias
Set II
New Minglewood Blues
Mississippi Half-Step Uptown Toodleloo
Samson & Delilah
Ship Of Fools
Dancing In The Street >
Wharf Rat >
Dancing In The Street >
Around & Around

Encore:
Johnny B. Goode

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
Donna Jean Godchaux - Vocals
